channel.description: https://soundcloud.com/that_dj_thomas/awake-on-saturday-night https://youtu.be/7Nsgbb9-9JQ You know those nights on Saturday where your either Partying, or struggling to fall asleep, or maybe your normal and all you do is sleep on Saturday night. Well, I did my best to re create those Saturday Night Vibes you get no matter how you spend your Saturday Night. Walking around downtown at 7pm, people eating dinner, walking around, half the stores are closed, a Man playing Saxophone trying to collect Money.
